txt.en: The last remaining spiders in Northern Mirkwood are in Torech Emel.
You have defeated many spiders in Torech Emel, making the realm of Eryn Lasgalen safer.
You have defeated many spiders in Torech Emel.
Torech Emel is found in the north-western reach of Eryn Lasgalen.\n\nYou should defeat any spiders you come across in Torech Emel.
A number of the spiders from Iphantemel's brood have taken refuge in the gorge of Torech Emel. You should defeat any spiders you come across in there.
